cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with the problem of multi-view sketch correspondence and proposes a deep learning approach to learn a novel local sketch descriptor from data. 
2. cs.GR (Graphics) is also a likely category as the paper involves generating multi-view line drawings from 3D shapes and designing a neural network to handle the sparsity and ambiguity of sketches. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper proposes a deep learning approach to learn the local sketch descriptor and the multi-branch neural network. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper involves developing a machine learning approach to solve a challenging problem in the field of computer vision. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with multi-view sketches and involves generating and processing visual data.
